values:
Be the Reds
FIFA 2010

I've finally decided not to strut about the internet practically nude (figuratively). 

So, I've made this a friends-only journal.

If you want to be my friend, go ahead; after all, in this country (the U.S.A), we have such a loose meaning of "friend."
 
Should you decide that you want to know what I ate at what time and how many calories it had and how many calories I burned scratching my bum and what I thought while I scratched my bum and how my thoughts digressed into remembering the dream I had last night about marrying a box of green tea and if you want to read my analysis of my dreams and such...

...then please, go ahead and leave a comment (below), or e-mail me with your livejournal username.
 
I am sorry for the inconvenience.
You probably know that I would rather be honest as my parents have unintentionally taught me.
